summary: An Ordinance providing for the condemnation and appropriation of portions of Sections Fourteen (14), Twenty-three (23) and Twenty-four (24), Township Twenty-four (24) North, Range Four (4) East, W. M.; and of Lots Twenty-three (23) and Twenty-four (24) and Twenty-five (25), B. W. John's & C. H. Hanford's Five Acre Tracts, all in the City of Seattle, for park and parkway purposes; and providing that the payment for the same be made from the Park Fund of the City of Seattle.
